<h2><span id=".E8.AA.9E.E6.96.87.E6.9C.83.28.EC.96.B4.EB.AC.B8.ED.9A.8C.29_4.E7.B4.9A.28.EA.B8.89.29II"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="語文會(어문회)_4級(급)II"><ruby class="hanja grade62"><rb>語文會</rb><rp>(</rp><rt>어문회</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> 4<ruby class="hanja grade60"><rb>級</rb><rp>(</rp><rt>급</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>II</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/index.php?title=%E8%AA%9E%E6%96%87%E6%9C%83_%E7%B4%9A%E6%95%B8%E5%88%A5_%E9%85%8D%E5%AE%9A%E6%BC%A2%E5%AD%97_%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%BD&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="부분 편집: 語文會(어문회) 4級(급)II">편집</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
